name: Advanced Auto & Truck Repair
tag_list: auto-repair-west-chester, trucks-repair-west-chester, transmission-repair-west-chester, auto-repair, trucks-repair, auto-repair-service, transmission-repair
overview:
Advanced Auto & Truck strides to gain the trust of their customers by treating them like family. They can handle most makes and models of cars, but their forte is trucks and heavy equipment. They have a wide variety of services, including PA state inspections, brakes, transmissions, tires, engine repair and more.

Though they have only been established in West Chester since 2007, their mechanics have decades of experience, and they are highly trained to specialize in trucks and heavy equipment. Advance Auto & Truck also makes custom parts in their shop to cut down on shipping time and get your vehicle back on the road faster. They make an effort to get your truck in and out as fast as possible because they know time in the shop is lost business for you. They strive to gain the trust of their customers, so they keep coming back.
